msgstr "実際に読み書きされたバイト数"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:896
#, kde-format
msgid "Show I/O rate"
msgstr "I/O の速度を表示"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:923
#, kde-format
msgid "Show Tooltips"
msgstr "ツールチップを表示"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1177
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"You do not have the permission to renice the process and there was a problem "
"trying to run as root."
msgstr ""
"プロセス優先度を変更する権限がありません。また、root として実行できませんでし"
"た。"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1203 ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1387
#, kde-format
msgid "You must select a process first."
msgstr "先にプロセスを選んでください。"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1328
#, fuzzy, kde-format
msgid ""
"You do not have the permission to change the I/O priority of the process and "
"there was a problem trying to run as root."
msgstr ""
"プロセスの I/O 優先度を変更する権限がありません。また、root として実行できま"
"せんでした。エラー %1 %2"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1344
#, fuzzy, kde-format
msgid ""
"You do not have the permission to change the CPU Scheduler for the process "
"and there was a problem trying to run as root."
msgstr ""
"プロセスの CPU スケジューラを変更する権限がありません。また、root として実行"
"できませんでした。エラー %1 %2"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1359
#, fuzzy, kde-format
msgid ""
"You do not have the permission to kill the process and there was a problem "
"trying to run as root."
msgstr ""
"プロセスを強制終了する権限がありません。また、root として実行できませんでし"
"た。"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1396
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to end this process?  Any unsaved work may be lost."
msgid_plural ""
"Are you sure you want to end these %1 processes?  Any unsaved work may be "
"lost"
msgstr[0] ""
"本当にこれら %1 個のプロセスを終了しますか？保存されていない作業は失われま"
"す。"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1399
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Dialog title"
msgid "End Process"
msgid_plural "End %1 Processes"
msgstr[0] "%1 個のプロセスを終了"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1401
#, kde-format
msgid "End"
msgstr "終了"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1403
#, fuzzy, kde-format
msgid ""
"<qt>Are you sure you want to <b>immediately and forcibly kill</b> this "
"process?  Any unsaved work may be lost."
msgid_plural ""
"<qt>Are you sure you want to <b>immediately and forcibly kill</b> these %1 "
"processes?  Any unsaved work may be lost"
msgstr[0] ""
"本当にこれら %1 個のプロセスを終了しますか？保存されていない作業は失われま"
"す。"

#. +> stable5
#: ksysguardprocesslist.cpp:1406
#, fuzzy, kde-format
msgctxt "Dialog title"
msgid "Forcibly Kill Process"
